DESCRIPTION:Weekly COO check-in (15 min).\n\nOpen your AI tool in your workspa
 ce and paste:\n\nRun the weekly check-in from the virtual-coo skill. Read com
 pany-state.md in this workspace for current context. Detect what changed sinc
 e the last check-in: new hires\, paying customers\, funding or fundraise prep.
 Check the stage-critical processes in the Duct Tape to COO wiki for your stag
 e and surface any that are slipping. Propose at most 3 next actions\, each wit
 h an owner\, a next step\, and the wiki page it came from. Ground everything i
 n the wiki. If something is not covered\, say so rather than inventing it. Upd
 ate company-state.md when done.
