  workspace and paste:\n\nRun the quarterly operational health check from the v
 irtual-coo skill. Read company-state.md in this workspace for stage\, revenue
 and funding context. Score every process that is critical or recommended at t
 he current stage on the 5 dimensions from the Duct Tape to COO framework. Ski
 p conditional processes that do not apply. Rank the gaps\, and for the top 3 t
 o 5 give wiki-backed fixes with owners. Flag any stage cells the wiki does not
